<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>09 - Install and Configure Nova on the Controller Node on Atlas</title><link>https://www.javiercd.es/en/posts/openstack/curso-openstack/instalacion-manual/09-instalacion-nova-nodo-controlador/</link><description>Recent content in 09 - Install and Configure Nova on the Controller Node on Atlas</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 23 Nov 2025 12:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.javiercd.es/en/posts/openstack/curso-openstack/instalacion-manual/09-instalacion-nova-nodo-controlador/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>09 - Install and configure Nova on the controller node</title><link>https://www.javiercd.es/en/posts/openstack/curso-openstack/instalacion-manual/09-instalacion-nova-nodo-controlador/09-instalacion-nova-nodo-controlador/</link><pubDate>Sun, 23 Nov 2025 12:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.javiercd.es/en/posts/openstack/curso-openstack/instalacion-manual/09-instalacion-nova-nodo-controlador/09-instalacion-nova-nodo-controlador/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;This document describes how to install and configure the Compute service (Nova) on the controller node (&lt;code&gt;controller01&lt;/code&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="prerequisites"&gt;Prerequisites&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Before starting, make sure you have the basic Keystone credentials and databases created (admin-openrc available).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="create-the-databases-on-controller01"&gt;Create the databases (on &lt;code&gt;controller01&lt;/code&gt;)&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Connect to the SQL server as &lt;code&gt;root&lt;/code&gt; to create the necessary databases:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;vagrant@controller01:~$ sudo mysql
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Create the &lt;code&gt;nova_api&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;nova&lt;/code&gt;, and &lt;code&gt;nova_cell0&lt;/code&gt; databases:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;CREATE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;DATABASE&lt;/span&gt; nova_api;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;CREATE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;DATABASE&lt;/span&gt; nova;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;CREATE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;DATABASE&lt;/span&gt; nova_cell0;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Grant permissions to the &lt;code&gt;nova&lt;/code&gt; account (replace &lt;code&gt;NOVA_DBPASS&lt;/code&gt; with your password):&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>